{"id":309592031,"lang":"python","lang_name":"Python","time":"3 years, 6 months","timestamp":1583417942,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"60 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/309592031/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"12 MB","code":"class Solution(object):\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s):\n        \"\"\"\n        :type s: str\n        :rtype: int\n        \"\"\"\n        summ = 0\n        ans = 0\n        nums = []\n        for char in s:\n            if not char in nums:\n                nums.append(char)\n                summ += 1\n                ans = max(ans, summ)\n            else:\n                idx = nums.index(char)\n                summ -= idx\n                nums = nums[idx + 1:]\n                nums.append(char)\n        return ans","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
